ww.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/depeche_mode_london_live_4-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/depeche_mode_london_live_4-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/depeche_mode_london_live_4-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/depeche-mode">Depeche Mode</a>昨晚（1 月 22 日星期一）在伦敦 O2 音乐厅拉开了他们 2024 年“Memento Mori”巡演的序幕。查看下面的照片、片段和歌单。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/depeche-mode-interview-memento-mori-dave-gahan-martin-gore-3410900">Depeche Mode 采访：“尽你所能——你不知道你是否会再次这样做”</a></strong></li></ul><p>昨晚是该乐队<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/depeche-mode-announce-2024-tour-dates-uk-ireland-europe-live-shows-buy-tickets-3466919">在英国、爱尔兰和欧洲进行的漫长舞台演出的</a>第一场演出，为支持他们的第 15 张也是最新专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/depeche-mode-memento-mori-review-3418286">《Memento Mori》</a>而进行巡回演出，也是他们<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/depeche-mode-live-in-london-twickenham-stadium-review-setlist-photos-3457601">自在伦敦广受好评的演出</a>以来在首都的首次约会。去年夏天的<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/depeche-mode-live-in-london-twickenham-stadium-review-setlist-photos-3457601">特威克纳姆体育场</a>。</p><p>在<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/nadine-shah">Nadine Shah</a>的支持下，乐队登上舞台，演奏了《Memento Mori》大气的开场曲《My Cosmos Is Mine》，雄心勃勃的舞台制作重复了灯光秀和 Anton Corbijn 体育场的视觉效果。 </p><figure id="attachment_3575583" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3575583" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3575583" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/depeche_mode_london_live_1.jpg" alt="Depeche Mode 在伦敦 The O2 现场演出（摄影：Gus Stewart/Redferns）" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/depeche_mode_london_live_1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/depeche_mode_london_live_1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/depeche_mode_london_live_1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/depeche_mode_london_live_1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/depeche_mode_london_live_1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/depeche_mode_london_live_1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3575583" class="wp-caption-text"> Depeche Mode 在伦敦 The O2 现场演出（摄影：Gus Stewart/Redferns） </figcaption></figure><figure id="attachment_3575584" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3575584" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3575584" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/depeche_mode_london_live_2.jpg" alt="Depeche Mode 在伦敦 The O2 现场演出（摄影：Gus Stewart/Redferns）" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/depeche_mode_london_live_2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/depeche_mode_london_live_2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/depeche_mode_london_live_2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/depeche_mode_london_live_2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/depeche_mode_london_live_2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/depeche_mode_london_live_2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3575584" class="wp-caption-text"> Depeche Mode 在伦敦 The O2 现场演出（摄影：Gus Stewart/Redferns）</figcaption></figure><p>主唱戴夫·加汉 (Dave Gahan) 在《Walking In My Shoes》中跳舞时充满活力，并展示了他的白色皮鞋，但除了感谢伦敦的接待和向“天使般”的歌声致敬之外，他在舞台上很少开玩笑。乐队成员<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/martin-gore">马丁·戈尔（Martin Gore）</a>在一段简短的原声部分中担任带头人。在精简的伴奏下，戈尔温柔地演唱了经典单曲《Strangelove》和上个月首映的粉丝最爱的《Heaven》版本——这两首歌曲都是由加汉在唱片中演唱的。</p><p>其他亮点包括他们惯常表演的《World In My Eyes》，向已故乐队成员安迪·弗莱彻 (Andy Fletcher) 致敬，安迪·弗莱彻<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/depeche-modes-andy-fletcher-has-died-at-the-age-of-60-3234836">于 2022 年在《Memento Mori》录制之前去世</a>，以及一系列热门歌曲，最终在安可的最后三重奏“Just Can&#39;t Get Enough”、“Never Let Me Down Again”和“Personal Jesus”。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Depeche Mode - Strangelove（马丁·戈尔独奏原声）（22/1/24，O2 Arena，伦敦，英国，英国）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/3JUwWlYeviU?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Depeche Mode - Heaven - 现场伦敦 O2 Arena - 2024 年 1 月 22 日" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/2wWzks-heNo?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Depeche Mode - Everything Counts（22/1/24，英国伦敦 O2 体育场）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/hJlDAWdQLC8?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Depeche Mode - Just Can&#39;t Get Enough（22/1/24，The O2 Arena，伦敦，英国，英国）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/QLfJUKJ_n48?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Depeche Mode @ The O2，伦敦 - 黑色庆典 - 2024 年 1 月 22 日" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/EUijpqMrNSc?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Depeche Mode @ The O2，伦敦 - Never Let Me Down Again - 2024 年 1 月 22 日" width="696"