0-combined.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/GreenDay-Saviors-outselling-UK-albums-chart-top-10-combined-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/GreenDay-Saviors-outselling-UK-albums-chart-top-10-combined-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/GreenDay-Saviors-outselling-UK-albums-chart-top-10-combined-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/GreenDay-Saviors-outselling-UK-albums-chart-top-10-combined-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/GreenDay-Saviors-outselling-UK-albums-chart-top-10-combined-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>目前， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/green-day">Green Day 的</a>销量超过了英国专辑榜前十名中的其他专辑以及<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/green-day-saviors-album-review-3567737">《Saviors》</a>的销量。</p><p>这对流行朋克三人组于上周五（1 月 19 日）发行了他们的第 14 张录音室唱片， <em>NME</em>在<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/green-day-saviors-album-review-3567737">四星评论</a>中称赞其为“他们自《美国白痴》以来最好的作品”。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/big-reads/green-day-interview-father-of-all-motherfuckers-2020-donald-trump-billie-eilish-2606230">《 <em>NME</em>大读物》——绿日：“我们过着我们一无所有的生活”</a></strong></li></ul><p>根据<a href="https://www.officialcharts.com/chart-news/green-day-saviors-number-1-album-midweek/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>官方排行榜</em></a>的最新更新，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/billie-joe-armstrong">比利·乔·阿姆斯特朗 (Billie Joe Armstrong)</a>等人。他们有望在本周五（1 月 26 日）下一次排行榜中夺得第五张英国冠军专辑。</p><p>截至周中，《救世主》的销量超过了前十名中其他歌曲的销量总和。</p><p>紧随 Green Day 进入前五名的是<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/neck-deep">Neck Deep</a>的同名专辑（排名第二）、Saxon 的《Hell, Fire And Damnation》（排名第三）、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/noah-kahan#:~:text=Shed%20Seven%20top%20albums%20chart,'re%20just%20getting%20started!%22https://www.nme.com/artists/noah-kahan#:~:text=Shed%20Seven%20top%20albums%20chart,'re%20just%20getting%20started!%22">Noah Kahan</a>的《Stick Season》（排名第四）和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-weeknd">The Weeknd</a>的“亮点”（第五）。</p><p>如果该团体取得胜利，《救世主》将继《美国白痴》（2004 年）、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/reviews-green-day-10417-335672#:~:text=Yet%20here%20it%20is%2C%20Green,swipe%20at%20our%20bloodthirsty%20decade.">《21 世纪崩溃》</a> （2009 年）、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/blogs/nme-blogs/fans-react-to-first-listen-of-green-days-revolution-radio-1188412">《革命电台》</a> （2016 年）和<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/green-day-father-of-all-review-2605870">《混蛋之父》</a> （2020 年）之后，在英国。</p><p>本周的官方排行榜将于周五下午 4 点（格林威治标准时间）在 BBC 广播 1 台现场直播。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Green Day - Bobby Sox（官方音乐视频）" width="696" height="522" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/NDjtguZG6iw?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/green-day-announce-2024-saviors-stadium-tour-including-huge-london-show-buy-tickets-3529041">Green Day 将于 5 月开始他们的 2024 年“Saviors”世界巡演</a>。继乐队在怀特岛音乐节上亮相之后，英国和爱尔兰的巡演包括六月在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/green-day-pet-shop-boys-and-the-prodigy-to-headline-isle-of-wight-festival-2024-lineup-buy-tickets-3528939#:~:text=Prodigy%20to%20headline-,Green%20Day%2C%20Pet%20Shop%20Boys%20and%20The%20Prodigy%20to,Isle%20Of%20Wight%20Festival%202024&amp;text=Isle%20Of%20Wight%20Festival%20has,Newport%20between%20June%2020%2D23.">温布利</a>体育场举行的大型演出。</p><p>上周， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/green-day-confirm-theyll-be-playing-dookie-and-american-idiot-in-full-on-2024-saviors-world-tour-3572429">Green Day 确认他们将在“Saviors”巡演中完整演奏《American Idiot》和《Dookie》，</a>分别纪念这两张经典专辑问世 20 周年和 30 周年。 <a href="https://www.ticketmaster.co.uk/green-day-tickets/artist/768353?irgwc=1&amp;utm_source=2862475-NME%20Networks%20Media%20Limited&amp;utm_medium=affiliate&amp;utm_campaign=2862475&amp;awtrc=&amp;clickId=x